data.meta_description:
21 likes, 0 comments - impetustechnologies on April 23, 2024: "Celebrating the incredible achievements of our Impetus - Delhi NCR team members! – Part 3
This video shines a light on Impetus team members in Delhi NCR who have reached major association milestones in their careers. We'll hear their stories and how Impetus' supportive culture has helped them grow.
Open communication is a cornerstone of Impetus, and these #CultureConversations showcase the strong bonds within our organization. Don't miss out on more inspiring stories to come! 
#LongAssociationAwards #EmployeeAppreciation #DelhiNCR #ImpetusFamily #CultureConversations".
